Quickstrike:





Quickstrike glared at Paralysis, but with a pleased look on his slim 
face. He looked around the area, with the heavy work going on. He 
remembered having ranks and jobs like that. And in surprise, he was 
glad to do things like that. It was because there was nothing else to 
do. 

He stared for a while. And to think, he had no complaints with his 
rank when the orignial Beast Wars was in place. Things were different 
now. Some things he didn't understand. 

"Well wanna show me where they are?" he asked Paralysis, almost in a 
demanding tone. He looked back and took a step forward. "Got any 
extra fliers? Dark Mouse might need uh lift here. Ah got here faster 
than she did. Figure that." He chuckled.
